data.text:
Mary Alden

ON THE REVERSE (but not shown): Warner Baxter

Period Paper is pleased to offer a great collection of original images from 1925, with short biographies, of "famous film folk." This collection, which includes the more obscure actors as well as the better known stars, is sure to be of interest to silent film buffs.

CONDITION

This 86+ year old Item is rated Very Fine. No creases. No tears. No water damage.

Product Type: Original Halftone Print; Grayscale

Grade: Very Fine

Dimensions: Approximately 4 x 7 inches; 10 x 18 cm

Authentication: Serial-Numbered Certificate of Authenticity w/ Full Provenance

Protection: Packaged in a custom archival sleeve with an acid-free black board (great for display, gift-giving, and preservation)

SILENT6C25
